O '''Yanosh Bogdan''', [[magyarikanes]]: ''János Bogdán'', ([[1963]] - [[9 Yanuara]] [[1999]]) sas ek [[rom]] andar i [[Ungariya]] so zhutisardyas but te kerel pes i [[Gandhi (mashkarutni shkola ando Pech)|Mashkarutni Shkola Gandhi]] katar o [[foro]] [[Pech]] (sas vi lako barideri, shero). 

Vov biyandilyas ando [[gav]] Görgeteg (sudestutni Ungariya), anda ek [[बयाश|bayash]] familiya. Ande Opralutne Shkole katar [[Seged]] thai [[Budapesht]] siklilyas filosofiya, [[magyarikani ćhib]], lekhavipen thai puranipen. Shirdyas (astardyas) te siklyarel ando [[Barch]]. Ando [[1992]]to bersh organizisardyas i Mashkarutni Shkola Gandhi (tar [[1994]] sas lako shero), i ekhto Romani mashkarutni shkola andar [[Europa]].

